@Backend_HostAddress = http://localhost:5236
@Token = <sätt din JWT efter login>

### Health
GET {{Backend_HostAddress}}/api/health

### Registrera
POST {{Backend_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "hemligt123",
  "displayName": "Testanvändare"
}

### Logga in
# @name login
POST {{Backend_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "hemligt123"
}

### Vänner (kräver Authorization: Bearer {{Token}})
GET {{Backend_HostAddress}}/api/friends
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}

###
GET {{Backend_HostAddress}}/api/friends/requests/received
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}

###
POST {{Backend_HostAddress}}/api/friends/request
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "toUserId": "guid-här"
}

### Sök användare
GET {{Backend_HostAddress}}/api/users/search?q=test
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}

### Skapa lobby (partyleader)
POST {{Backend_HostAddress}}/api/gamesessions
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "gameType": 0,
  "maxPlayers": 6
}

### Mina sessioner
GET {{Backend_HostAddress}}/api/gamesessions
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}

### Byta kortspel (partyleader)
PATCH {{Backend_HostAddress}}/api/gamesessions/{{sessionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "gameType": 1
}

### Starta spel (partyleader)
POST {{Backend_HostAddress}}/api/gamesessions/{{sessionId}}/start
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}
